          - Fresh battle system. It is turn based but feels like an     
          action                                                        
          - Hundreds of units. And you can get anyone to your team      
            (even foes)                                                 
          - Humorous plot and unique description of every game element  
          - RPG-elements like inventory and unit classes                
          - Units evolution and selection of specialization on every    
